---
// src/components/YouthSupport.astro
---
<section class="section-dark py-20 sm:py-28">
  <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-5 sm:px-8 lg:px-12">
    
    <div class="text-center mb-12">
      <span class="gold-line mx-auto"></span>
      <h1 class="section-heading text-4xl sm:text-5xl text-white mb-4">
        Youth &amp; Family Support
      </h1>
      <p class="font-body text-amber-400 text-lg">Mdantsane</p>
    </div>

    <div class="prose prose-invert max-w-none text-gray-300 text-lg leading-relaxed mb-12">
      <p>
        Beyond events and celebrations, eKoneni has become a quiet pillar in the community. We regularly support local youth programmes and assist families going through difficult times with groceries, school supplies, and emotional support.
      </p>
      <p>
        For many young people in Mdantsane, the lounge is more than a place to party — it has become a space of belonging, guidance, and real care. This is the deeper purpose behind everything we do.
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="mb-12">
      <div class="aspect-video bg-zinc-900 rounded-2xl overflow-hidden border border-amber-400/10 flex items-center justify-center">
        <img src="https://placehold.co/1200x630/1f2937/9ca3af?text=Insert+Youth+Support+Photos+&+Videos" 
             alt="Placeholder - Youth & Family Support" class="w-full h-full object-cover">
      </div>
      <p class="text-center text-sm text-gray-500 mt-3">Insert real photos and videos here</p>
    </div>

    <div class="text-center">
      <a href="#contact" class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 px-8 py-3.5 rounded-full bg-amber-400 text-black font-medium tracking-wide text-sm hover:bg-amber-300 transition-colors">
        Support this initiative →
      </a>
      <p class="mt-4 text-sm text-gray-400">
        <a href="/community" class="hover:text-amber-400 transition-colors">← Back to Community Stories</a>
      </p>
    </div>

  </div>
</section>